d the same analysis on a subsample of 32 objects, already\nselected for supporting the NIKA2 SZ Large Program.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2020 20:16:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 21:24:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-10"}
