ancy between $dc$ and $ac$ conductivity, but also provides a\nscenario to explain the presence of quantum oscillations in magnetization in\nthe absence of quantum oscillations in electrical resistivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2020 01:30:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-09"}
