d to be high and might significantly contribute to the higher\nspin parameters. We find significantly later formation epochs for void\ngalaxies; this should give lower matter densities and may imply lower surface\ndensities of disk galaxies. Thus, void galaxies have higher spin parameters and\nlater formation epochs; both are factors that may increase the probability of\nforming LSBGs in voids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2020 03:00:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Jun 2021 13:14:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-22"}
